====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# [[salt]]; [[salty]] substance, especially [[table salt]]
#: {{zh-x|鹽 放 多 了。|Too much '''salt''' is added.}}
#* {{zh-x|厥 貢 鹽 絺，海 物 惟 錯。|Its articles of tribute were '''salt''', fine cloth of dolichos fibre, productions of the sea of various kinds.|ref=Shangshu}}
# {{lb|zh|chemistry}} [[salt]]
# {{lb|zh|Southern Min}} [[food]] [[product]] [[pickled]] with salt
# {{lb|zh|Southern Min}} [[sweat]] [[stain]]; salt [[efflorescence]]
# {{lb|zh|cryptography}} [[salt]]
#: {{zh-x|沒有 加鹽 的 密碼 容易 被 破解。|Passwords that are not '''salted''' are easily cracked.}}

